data.description: Live the Bungalow Lifestyle in this 2 bedroom 1 bath home. This bungalow is truly charming, from the moment you walk in you enter a warm and inviting living room with a an eat-in-nook. There is a formal dining area and a great cooks kitchen. The bathroom is equipped with a jacuzzi tub, for a spa-like retreat. The master is spacious with a sitting area, perfect to relax and read a book or watch your favorite movie. The backyard has a large storage shed and plenty of room to roam. Some of the recent upgrades include framing, windows, roof, septic tank and drain field, electrical switches, outlets, bathroom sinks, 36"X72" Jacuzzi tub, custom tile, tankless water heater, AC unit and a water purification system, all updated within the last 5 years. The only thing missing from this Bungalow is YOU!
